一直想发财、<span class="_ _10"></span>发财。<span class="_ _10"></span>结果就算你发了财，<span class="_ _10"></span>但真的幸福吗？</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y165 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">刚开始两三天也许稍微有点感觉，<span class="_ _5"></span>但久了以后，<span class="_ _5"></span>只有层出不</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y29f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">穷的烦恼，<span class="_ _3"></span>不一定有轻松和自在。<span class="_ _7"></span>同样，<span class="_ _3"></span>感情、<span class="_ _7"></span>地位等给你</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
